al .agents/ workflow and rules contents from all 9 repos (keep directory for symlink step).\",\n          \"targetFile\": \"/Users/ryan/development/common_bond/antigravity-environment/\",\n          \"completedAt\": null,\n          \"completedBy\": null\n        },\n        {\n          \"taskId\": \"ARCH-01-T4\",\n          \"status\": \"open\",\n          \"description\": \"Create symlinks: planner-frontend/.agents -> frontend-nextjs, preference-frontend/.agents -> frontend-nextjs, workforce-frontend/.agents -> frontend-nextjs, website-frontend/.agents -> frontend-nextjs, supabase-receptor/.agents -> supabase-infrastructure, match-backend/.agents -> backend-python, receptor-planner/.agents -> backend-python, common-bond/.agents -> docusaurus.\",\n          \"targetFile\": \"/Users/ryan/development/common_bond/antigravity-environment/\",\n          \"completedAt\": null,\n          \"completedBy\": null\n        },\n        {\n          \"taskId\": \"ARCH-01-T5\",\n          \"status\": \"open\",\n          \"description\": \"Add .agents to .gitignore in each of the 9 child repos.\",\n          \"targetFile\": \"/Users/ryan/development/common_bond/antigravity-environment/\",\n          \"completedAt\": null,\n          \"completedBy\": null\n        }\n      ],\n      \"severity_history\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ARCH-02\",\n      \"severity\": \"critical\",\n      \"status\": \"open\",\n      \"category\": \"Process Gap\",\n      \"repo\": \"dev-environment\",\n      \"area\": \".agents directory structure\",\n      \"description\": \"dev-environment/.agents/ has no category-level organisation. Workflow files with category-specific context live in individual repos rather than in a shared canonical location.\",\n      \"tasks\": [\n        {\n          \"taskId\": \"ARCH-02-T1\",\n          \"status\": \"open\",\n          \"description\": \"Addressed by ARCH-01-T1 and ARCH-01-T2 — no separate tasks required.\",\n          \"targetFile\": \"/Users/ryan/